# --- Vector Database & Local Data ---
# We keep the 'db' folder structure but ignore the actual data files 
# to ensure everyone starts with a fresh or controlled index.
# If you want judges to have your pre-indexed data, comment these out.
backend/db/*.sqlite3
backend/db/**/*.bin

